All Implemented Interfaces:
NodeVisitor<SoyNode,Void>
public class RenderVisitor
extends AbstractSoyNodeVisitor<Void>

Visitor for rendering the template subtree rooted at a given SoyNode.

Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).

AbstractNodeVisitor.exec(N) should be called on a template, and the data passed to the constructor should of course be appropriate for the called template. The rendered output will be appended to the outputSb provided to the constructor.
